                                            [Cracked]


## Description

Face4Pass is an application that allows you to easily create photos for your documents (i.e passport).

Drag and drop or open an existing file.
Take a photo with the built-in iSight camera.
Edit many parameters of the image (exposure, contrast, saturation, temperature, tint, sharpness).
Automatically improve the quality of the image.
For optimum sizing of the photo, you can use the grid and the zoom in/out function.
Erase the unwanted part of your photo (i.e. remove the background).
Print from 1 to 12 copies in size 2x2 inches or 3.5x4.5 cm. 
Generate a preview in pdf format.
Print in A4/A5/A6 paper size.
Export the file as PDF/PNG/TIFF/JPEG/JP2/BMP/GIF format.
Save your template on iCloud.

Conform to the ISO/IEC JTC 1/SC 37 N 506 specifications (Biometric Data Interchange Formats).
